FIRST: RUN cmd/bash on the project folder
second : setup nodejs files by run comand $npm init
third : from npmjs.com choose packets you need and thire version then install them by run like this:
	 $npm install --save express@4.16.3 (version)
	 $npm install mysql@2.15.2 (version)
	 $npm install bodyparser@1.18.2 (version)
	 $npm install -g nodemon // after apply it do $nodemon index.js then after any change in index.js it apply automaticly
	 $npm install postman // for use and run query such as DELETE

forth : download and install (MYSQL workbench) for build MySql DataBase and tables as we need.
	or use php.myadmin with examp server
